{"tid":337960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個比朋友賣既經歷","createTime":"2017-07-27T18:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T21:46:58.000Z","uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23e83b60ebe7ce93a08e54dbd95eb5c83ee03a58","tid":337960,"uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:10:47.000Z","msg":"果陣第一年入u   細o同組女仔 開頭幾純品又搞笑<br />\n翻學順路日日一齊返 做埋莊員<br />\n當正佢係心腹 對佢毫無保留 <br />\n最後 發現原來一直佢是非當人情 我同佢講既野一路都只不過係佢買更多是非既交易品<br />\n而家對住佢真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入到u先知 有d人有d說話真係唔洗擺上心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：朋友大過天 對朋友一定好 公認"},{"pid":"af2f8f1418f619e950bf80505318e9d71c80f6e2","tid":337960,"uid":96511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:14:47.000Z","msg":"成日比人賣比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔撚再會對人咁毫無保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab8c9732f24b1c2e3260175a5108e718cfae161","tid":337960,"uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日比人賣比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔撚再會對人咁毫無保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人賣過d咩呀巴打"},{"pid":"23f529a423ea1a36cded28f92158c226a81d9169","tid":337960,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 永遠得我有義氣<br />\n我出事無人理"},{"pid":"a9184eab96edc06382c62410c227845b0a9a6b72","tid":337960,"uid":96511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日比人賣比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔撚再會對人咁毫無保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人賣過d咩呀巴打</blockquote><br />\n好朋友收收埋埋瞞住我做左好多嘢<br />\n透過人地把口我先知<br />\n覺得自己好撚犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n信佢先乜都講最後比人賣到一乾二淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861ac980ec22a7f4ef6d49e933e5f6de013d1223","tid":337960,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d745f421de507cec21bdec01d5900c7918197f","tid":337960,"uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 永遠得我有義氣<br />\n我出事無人理</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過睇清乜人好事"},{"pid":"12a1cbccd649c59ad5e44e457accd5bec6ba5c4c","tid":337960,"uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日比人賣比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔撚再會對人咁毫無保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人賣過d咩呀巴打</blockquote><br />\n好朋友收收埋埋瞞住我做左好多嘢<br />\n透過人地把口我先知<br />\n覺得自己好撚犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">信佢先乜都講最後比人賣到一乾二淨#</span>yup#</blockquote><br />\n呢樣先最傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想信人"},{"pid":"94720e5ac7340d51122ec34219a66f7f93cc443b","tid":337960,"uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女＞兄弟  常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class