ckquote>賣朋友算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次行啲地攤見到有檔玩咩緣份game<br />\n個fd話想填咪陪下佢<br />\n然後有一欄係認為自己似咩動物<br />\nfd : 我諗唔到，你覺得我似乜？<br />\n我 : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 智障<br />\nfd : <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係有依種動物？<br />\n我 : <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀哺乳類黎，你唔知咩？<br />\n然後佢照填左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜鳩呀⋯"},{"pid":"f52cbb3498d76ab5af0565f2a44fac33d07f10c7","tid":337960,"uid":37185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T19:18:54.000Z","msg":"最緊要走得快<br />\n<br />\n中學有個frd成日傳我是非<br />\n最on9唔撚係真<br />\n<br />\n話我咩食減肥藥 學校睇咸網 比人暗戀（搞到我好驚疏遠左個個人）<br />\n<br />\n唔明佢咩心態 知道左表面繼續扮frd<br />\n暗地裡明晒咩事心諗你繼續吹"},{"pid":"17fee2f049aa602f91cf5af16c7663490f10eb8a","tid":337960,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"好多年前嘅事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次約左成大班人（連埋我13個人）<br />\n咁我地習慣左要一張長枱 坐埋哂同一邊嘅<br />\n咁好地地飲下紅酒食下野啦<br />\n點知食食下飯 <br />\n其中一條友無啦啦走過嚟錫左我一啖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住就有一大堆官兵沖入嚟捉走左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講佢收左人幾蚊就賣左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d23d61b81603acdd8fcf0b0c0135b162fd7e91","tid":337960,"uid":20073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T20:27:38.000Z","msg":"試過去東京旅行<br />\n個fd同佢女朋友分開機黎<br />\n咁佢要離隊去拍拖，我地係新宿站分開既時候佢就講<br />\n：屌你地仲企係到做咩，走啦我條女唔撚想見到你地。最尾比佢賣左係人生路不熟既新宿站外面。"},{"pid":"b883d2cef350f4c83e766d66e952609ce5b5ce8f","tid":337960,"uid":48084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T20:50:20.000Z","msg":"比人屈算唔算<br />\n中學有fd周圍放流料屈尻我嘅人格<br />\n同埋老師講我做功課請槍<br />\n後尾我病左一排冇返學<br />\n就周圍同人講我比老師發現左請槍所以唔夠膽返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢講嘅野全部都係假嘅<br />\n搞到全班同老師都排擠我<br />\n返到學果陣第1事問我病左堅定流<br />\n冇人信我真係病左<br />\n不過我都冇理佢，繼續同佢扮fd<br />\n過多幾年佢吹太多水，得罪唔少人<br />\n搞到佢大半中學生活比人排擠，又還返我清白<br />\n真係心都涼哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿相認"},{"pid":"960d197dd174471dcde2d4aa0825a57b08a0b42a","tid":337960,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T21:44:12.000Z","msg":"自己不嬲唔係好講自己野<br />\n知我啲嘢既人都無四圍講<br />\n覺得自己都幾識睇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5ad33f9c545b07859cd11815aa388097facfc9","tid":337960,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T21:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女＞兄弟  常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女＞兄弟 <br />\n呢啲人你最好同佢保持距離<br />\n好極有限"}]}